data.title: Texas Senate Election Results: Beto O’Rourke vs. Ted Cruz

* Incumbent

See all Texas results ›

Ted Cruz, the incumbent Republican senator from the Lone Star State, has defeated Beto O’Rourke, the Democratic challenger. The maverick campaign, with Mr. O’Rourke’s tour of all 254 Texas counties and $70 million in campaign contributions, received enormous national attention as a political underdog story.
